Sentence is withheld and the defendant is placed on probation to DOC for three (3) years, consecutive to the prison sentences presently being served on case no: 16 CF 454, to commence on defendant's discharge date after extended supervision ends.
Conditions of probation:
1) Pay court costs;
2) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC;
3) assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process;
4) maintain absolute sobriety and have no possession or consumption of illegal drugs, unless prescribed and taken in prescribed doses;
5) have no contact with Richard Krueger, his residence and place of business without the agents approval;
6) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
7) AODA assessment and follow through.
Minutes.
